DOMTextRun.characters: This is a mod loader for armed with wings rearmed. All mods are saved in the AWW_Mods folder. Current support for others to mod the game is bad and will be improved on in the future. A guide will be coming out soon for modding. - You can choose mods to enable/disable in the mods menu after pressing the "MODS" button.
